{"id": "figure_015", "modality": "figures", "name": "Evoformer (AlphaFold MSA + Pair Representation)", "task": {"description": "Create a single 1920x1080 self-contained HTML file using ONLY inline CSS and inline SVG that reproduces an AlphaFold-style Evoformer block figure. Title 'Evoformer Block (x48)' at top in 32px bold with the '48 blocks' multiplier shown. The block operates on TWO representations side by side: a LEFT 'MSA Representation (s x r x c_m)' drawn as a stacked grid (rows = sequences, columns = residues) and a RIGHT 'Pair Representation (r x r x c_z)' drawn as a square residue-by-residue grid. MSA-side sub-modules stacked vertically: 'MSA Row-wise Gated Self-Attention (with pair bias)', 'MSA Column-wise Gated Self-Attention', 'MSA Transition'. Pair-side sub-modules: 'Outer Product Mean' (arrow FROM MSA INTO the pair representation), 'Triangle Multiplicative Update (outgoing)', 'Triangle Multiplicative Update (incoming)', 'Triangle Self-Attention (starting node)', 'Triangle Self-Attention (ending node)', 'Pair Transition'. Draw the 'pair bias' arrow FROM the pair representation INTO the MSA row attention, and the 'Outer Product Mean' arrow FROM the MSA INTO the pair representation, making the two representations communicate bidirectionally. Show the '(x48)' block repetition. HARDEN (density + alignment): ALSO include (a) a LEGEND box that maps every distinct block color and every arrow/line style used in the figure, and (b) a small tensor-shape annotation on each major block (e.g. 'BxNxd'). Pack the figure densely with at least 14 labeled elements; every group of sibling blocks must be equal-size and share edges, with uniform gutters, and nothing may overlap or clip.", "requirements": ["Both representations (MSA grid and Pair grid) and ALL named sub-modules (3 MSA-side, 6 pair-side including Outer Product Mean) are visible with no clipping at any edge", "No two boxes overlap each other", "Every sub-module label and dimension annotation (s x r x c_m, r x r x c_z) is fully contained inside its box with no overflow", "The MSA Representation is drawn as a sequences-by-residues grid and the Pair Representation as a square residue-by-residue grid, visually distinct", "The 'pair bias' arrow runs FROM the pair representation INTO the MSA row-wise attention module", "The 'Outer Product Mean' arrow runs FROM the MSA representation INTO the pair representation", "Both triangle multiplicative updates (outgoing and incoming) and both triangle self-attentions (starting and ending node) are present and distinctly labelled", "The '(x48)' block-repetition multiplier is shown and does not overlap any box", "Communication arrows (pair bias, outer product mean) do not pass through unrelated sub-module boxes", "MSA-side sub-modules are evenly stacked and pair-side sub-modules are evenly stacked (aligned columns)", "No element is within 10px of any viewport edge", "No horizontal or vertical scrollbar appears; all content fits inside 1920x1080", "A legend box maps every block color and arrow/line style used; each major block carries a tensor-shape annotation; sibling blocks are equal-size and edge-aligned with uniform gutters; no element overlaps or is clipped"]}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 6362, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 6704}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 5618, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 6841}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 1, "ss_text_overlap": 1, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 5895, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 6409}], "ss_img": "images/figures/figure_015_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/figures/figure_015_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Evoformer Block Architecture</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1880px;\n            height: 1040px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <svg width=\"1880\" height=\"1040\" viewBox=\"0 0 1880 1040\">\n            <!-- Background -->\n            <rect width=\"1880\" height=\"1040\" fill=\"#f8f9fa\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Title -->\n            <text x=\"940\" y=\"40\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"32\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1a1a1a\">\n                Evoformer Block (\u00d748)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Main Block Container -->\n            <rect x=\"80\" y=\"80\" width=\"1600\" height=\"800\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"880\" y=\"105\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                Single Evoformer Block\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- MSA Representation Side -->\n            <g id=\"msa-side\">\n                <!-- MSA Representation -->\n                <rect x=\"120\" y=\"140\" width=\"280\" height=\"180\" fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"260\" y=\"165\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    MSA Representation\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"260\" y=\"185\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#34495e\">\n                    (s \u00d7 r \u00d7 c_m)\n                </text>\n                \n                <!-- MSA Grid Visualization -->\n                <g id=\"msa-grid\">\n                    <rect x=\"140\" y=\"200\" width=\"240\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#bde3ff\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n                    <!-- Grid lines for sequences -->\n                    <line x1=\"140\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"380\" y2=\"220\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"140\" y1=\"240\" x2=\"380\" y2=\"240\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"140\" y1=\"260\" x2=\"380\" y2=\"260\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"140\" y1=\"280\" x2=\"380\" y2=\"280\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                    <!-- Grid lines for residues -->\n                    <line x1=\"180\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"180\" y2=\"300\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"220\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"220\" y2=\"300\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"260\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"260\" y2=\"300\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"300\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"300\" y2=\"300\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"340\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"340\" y2=\"300\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                </g>\n                \n                <!-- MSA Row-wise Attention -->\n                <rect x=\"120\" y=\"350\" width=\"280\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#fff3cd\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"260\" y=\"375\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    MSA Row-wise Gated\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"260\" y=\"395\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Self-Attention\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"260\" y=\"415\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#34495e\">\n                    (s \u00d7 r \u00d7 c_m) + pair bias\n                </text>\n                \n                <!-- MSA Column-wise Attention -->\n                <rect x=\"120\" y=\"450\" width=\"280\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#d4edda\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"260\" y=\"475\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    MSA Column-wise Gated\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"260\" y=\"495\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Self-Attention\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"260\" y=\"515\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#34495e\">\n                    (s \u00d7 r \u00d7 c_m)\n                </text>\n                \n                <!-- MSA Transition -->\n                <rect x=\"120\" y=\"550\" width=\"280\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#f8d7da\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"260\" y=\"580\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    MSA Transition\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"260\" y=\"605\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#34495e\">\n                    (s \u00d7 r \u00d7 c_m)\n                </text>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- Pair Representation Side -->\n            <g id=\"pair-side\">\n                <!-- Pair Representation -->\n                <rect x=\"1200\" y=\"140\" width=\"280\" height=\"180\" fill=\"#f0e6ff\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"165\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Pair Representation\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"185\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#34495e\">\n                    (r \u00d7 r \u00d7 c_z)\n                </text>\n                \n                <!-- Pair Grid Visualization -->\n                <g id=\"pair-grid\">\n                    <rect x=\"1220\" y=\"200\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" fill=\"#d7bde2\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n                    <!-- Grid lines -->\n                    <line x1=\"1240\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"1240\" y2=\"320\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"1260\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"1260\" y2=\"320\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"1280\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"1280\" y2=\"320\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"1300\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"1300\" y2=\"320\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"1320\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"1320\" y2=\"320\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"1220\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"1340\" y2=\"220\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"1220\" y1=\"240\" x2=\"1340\" y2=\"240\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"1220\" y1=\"260\" x2=\"1340\" y2=\"260\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"1220\" y1=\"280\" x2=\"1340\" y2=\"280\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"1220\" y1=\"300\" x2=\"1340\" y2=\"300\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                </g>\n                \n                <!-- Outer Product Mean -->\n                <rect x=\"1200\" y=\"350\" width=\"280\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#e1f5fe\" stroke=\"#00bcd4\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"375\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Outer Product Mean\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"395\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#34495e\">\n                    (r \u00d7 r \u00d7 c_z)\n                </text>\n                \n                <!-- Triangle Updates -->\n                <rect x=\"1200\" y=\"430\" width=\"135\" height=\"70\" fill=\"#fff8e1\" stroke=\"#ff9800\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"1267\" y=\"450\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Triangle Mult.\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1267\" y=\"470\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Update\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1267\" y=\"485\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#34495e\">\n                    (outgoing)\n                </text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"1345\" y=\"430\" width=\"135\" height=\"70\" fill=\"#fff8e1\" stroke=\"#ff9800\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"1412\" y=\"450\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Triangle Mult.\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1412\" y=\"470\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Update\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1412\" y=\"485\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#34495e\">\n                    (incoming)\n                </text>\n                \n                <!-- Triangle Self-Attention -->\n                <rect x=\"1200\" y=\"520\" width=\"135\" height=\"70\" fill=\"#e8f5e8\" stroke=\"#4caf50\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"1267\" y=\"540\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Triangle\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1267\" y=\"560\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Self-Attention\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1267\" y=\"575\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#34495e\">\n                    (start node)\n                </text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"1345\" y=\"520\" width=\"135\" height=\"70\" fill=\"#e8f5e8\" stroke=\"#4caf50\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"1412\" y=\"540\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Triangle\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1412\" y=\"560\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Self-Attention\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1412\" y=\"575\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#34495e\">\n                    (end node)\n                </text>\n                \n                <!-- Pair Transition -->\n                <rect x=\"1200\" y=\"610\" width=\"280\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#fce4ec\" stroke=\"#e91e63\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"635\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Pair Transition\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"655\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#34495e\">\n                    (r \u00d7 r \u00d7 c_z)\n                </text>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- Communication Arrows -->\n            <!-- Pair bias arrow (Pair -> MSA Row Attention) -->\n            <defs>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                </marker>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead-blue\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#3498db\"/>\n                </marker>\n            </defs>\n            \n            <!-- Pair bias arrow -->\n            <path d=\"M 1200 390 Q 940 350 400 390\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"800\" y=\"340\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9b59b6\">\n                pair bias\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Outer Product Mean arrow -->\n            <path d=\"M 400 380 Q 660 340 1200 380\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#00bcd4\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-blue)\"/>\n            <text x=\"800\" y=\"320\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#00bcd4\">\n                outer product\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Central Communication Hub -->\n            <rect x=\"500\" y=\"350\" width=\"600\" height=\"280\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"800\" y=\"375\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#34495e\">\n                Bidirectional Communication\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Residual Connections -->\n            <g id=\"residual-connections\">\n                <!-- MSA residuals -->\n                <path d=\"M 100 230 Q 80 230 80 390 Q 80 490 100 490\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#7f8c8d\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n                <path d=\"M 100 490 Q 80 490 80 590 Q 80 590 100 590\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#7f8c8d\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n                \n                <!-- Pair residuals -->\n                <path d=\"M 1500 230 Q 1520 230 1520 380 Q 1520 465 1500 465\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#7f8c8d\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n                <path d=\"M 1500 465 Q 1520 465 1520 555 Q 1520 640 1500 640\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#7f8c8d\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- Block Repetition Indicator -->\n            <rect x=\"1520\" y=\"80\" width=\"140\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#95a5a6\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n            <text x=\"1590\" y=\"105\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                Repeat \u00d748\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"1590\" y=\"125\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#34495e\">\n                blocks\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Legend -->\n            <g id=\"legend\">\n                <rect x=\"80\" y=\"900\" width=\"800\" height=\"120\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"90\" y=\"920\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Legend</text>\n                \n                <!-- Color Legend -->\n                <rect x=\"100\" y=\"930\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#3498db\"/>\n                <text x=\"130\" y=\"942\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">MSA Representation</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"100\" y=\"950\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#fff3cd\" stroke=\"#f39c12\"/>\n                <text x=\"130\" y=\"962\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">MSA Row Attention</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"100\" y=\"970\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#d4edda\" stroke=\"#27ae60\"/>\n                <text x=\"130\" y=\"982\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">MSA Column Attention</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"100\" y=\"990\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#f8d7da\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\"/>\n                <text x=\"130\" y=\"1002\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">MSA Transition</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"300\" y=\"930\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#f0e6ff\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\"/>\n                <text x=\"330\" y=\"942\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Pair Representation</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"300\" y=\"950\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#e1f5fe\" stroke=\"#00bcd4\"/>\n                <text x=\"330\" y=\"962\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Outer Product Mean</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"300\" y=\"970\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#fff8e1\" stroke=\"#ff9800\"/>\n                <text x=\"330\" y=\"982\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Triangle Updates</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"300\" y=\"990\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#e8f5e8\" stroke=\"#4caf50\"/>\n                <text x=\"330\" y=\"1002\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Triangle Attention</text>\n                \n                <!-- Arrow Legend -->\n                <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"940\" x2=\"540\" y2=\"940\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                <text x=\"550\" y=\"945\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Pair Bias</text>\n                \n                <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"960\" x2=\"540\" y2=\"960\" stroke=\"#00bcd4\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-blue)\"/>\n                <text x=\"550\" y=\"965\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Outer Product</text>\n                \n                <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"980\" x2=\"540\" y2=\"980\" stroke=\"#7f8c8d\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n                <text x=\"550\" y=\"985\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Residual Connection</text>\n                \n                <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"1000\" x2=\"540\" y2=\"1000\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\"/>\n                <text x=\"550\" y=\"1005\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Communication Zone</text>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- Tensor Shape Annotations -->\n            <text x=\"90\" y=\"680\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">s = sequences</text>\n            <text x=\"90\" y=\"695\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">r = residues</text>\n            <text x=\"90\" y=\"710\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">c_m = MSA channels</text>\n            <text x=\"90\" y=\"725\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">c_z = pair channels</text>\n        </svg>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Evoformer Block Architecture</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1880px;\n            height: 1040px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <svg width=\"1880\" height=\"1040\" viewBox=\"0 0 1880 1040\">\n            <!-- Background -->\n            <rect width=\"1880\" height=\"1040\" fill=\"#f8f9fa\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Title -->\n            <text x=\"940\" y=\"50\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"32\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1a1a1a\">\n                Evoformer Block (\u00d748)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Main Block Container -->\n            <rect x=\"100\" y=\"100\" width=\"1480\" height=\"780\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" rx=\"10\"/>\n            <text x=\"840\" y=\"125\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                Single Evoformer Block\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- MSA Representation Side -->\n            <g id=\"msa-side\">\n                <!-- MSA Representation -->\n                <rect x=\"140\" y=\"160\" width=\"280\" height=\"200\" fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n                <text x=\"280\" y=\"185\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    MSA Representation\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"280\" y=\"205\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#34495e\">\n                    (s \u00d7 r \u00d7 c_m)\n                </text>\n                \n                <!-- Grid visualization for MSA -->\n                <g stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\">\n                    <line x1=\"160\" y1=\"230\" x2=\"400\" y2=\"230\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"160\" y1=\"250\" x2=\"400\" y2=\"250\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"160\" y1=\"270\" x2=\"400\" y2=\"270\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"160\" y1=\"290\" x2=\"400\" y2=\"290\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"160\" y1=\"310\" x2=\"400\" y2=\"310\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"160\" y1=\"330\" x2=\"400\" y2=\"330\"/>\n                    \n                    <line x1=\"180\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"180\" y2=\"340\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"220\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"220\" y2=\"340\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"260\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"260\" y2=\"340\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"300\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"300\" y2=\"340\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"340\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"340\" y2=\"340\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"380\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"380\" y2=\"340\"/>\n                </g>\n                <text x=\"150\" y=\"255\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">sequences</text>\n                <text x=\"280\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">residues</text>\n                \n                <!-- MSA Row-wise Attention -->\n                <rect x=\"140\" y=\"390\" width=\"280\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#fff3cd\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"280\" y=\"415\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    MSA Row-wise Gated\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"280\" y=\"435\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Self-Attention\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"280\" y=\"450\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#34495e\">\n                    (with pair bias)\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"280\" y=\"465\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">\n                    s\u00d7r\u00d7c_m \u2192 s\u00d7r\u00d7c_m\n                </text>\n                \n                <!-- MSA Column-wise Attention -->\n                <rect x=\"140\" y=\"490\" width=\"280\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#d1ecf1\" stroke=\"#17a2b8\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"280\" y=\"515\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    MSA Column-wise Gated\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"280\" y=\"535\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Self-Attention\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"280\" y=\"555\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">\n                    s\u00d7r\u00d7c_m \u2192 s\u00d7r\u00d7c_m\n                </text>\n                \n                <!-- MSA Transition -->\n                <rect x=\"140\" y=\"590\" width=\"280\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#d4edda\" stroke=\"#28a745\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"280\" y=\"620\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    MSA Transition\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"280\" y=\"645\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">\n                    s\u00d7r\u00d7c_m \u2192 s\u00d7r\u00d7c_m\n                </text>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- Pair Representation Side -->\n            <g id=\"pair-side\">\n                <!-- Pair Representation -->\n                <rect x=\"1200\" y=\"160\" width=\"280\" height=\"200\" fill=\"#fce4ec\" stroke=\"#e91e63\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"185\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Pair Representation\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"205\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#34495e\">\n                    (r \u00d7 r \u00d7 c_z)\n                </text>\n                \n                <!-- Grid visualization for Pair -->\n                <g stroke=\"#e91e63\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\">\n                    <line x1=\"1230\" y1=\"230\" x2=\"1450\" y2=\"230\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"1230\" y1=\"250\" x2=\"1450\" y2=\"250\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"1230\" y1=\"270\" x2=\"1450\" y2=\"270\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"1230\" y1=\"290\" x2=\"1450\" y2=\"290\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"1230\" y1=\"310\" x2=\"1450\" y2=\"310\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"1230\" y1=\"330\" x2=\"1450\" y2=\"330\"/>\n                    \n                    <line x1=\"1250\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"1250\" y2=\"340\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"1290\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"1290\" y2=\"340\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"1330\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"1330\" y2=\"340\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"1370\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"1370\" y2=\"340\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"1410\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"1410\" y2=\"340\"/>\n                    <line x1=\"1450\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"1450\" y2=\"340\"/>\n                </g>\n                <text x=\"1210\" y=\"255\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">residue i</text>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">residue j</text>\n                \n                <!-- Triangle Multiplicative Update (outgoing) -->\n                <rect x=\"1200\" y=\"390\" width=\"280\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#f8d7da\" stroke=\"#dc3545\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"415\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Triangle Multiplicative Update\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"430\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    (outgoing)\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"445\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">\n                    r\u00d7r\u00d7c_z \u2192 r\u00d7r\u00d7c_z\n                </text>\n                \n                <!-- Triangle Multiplicative Update (incoming) -->\n                <rect x=\"1200\" y=\"470\" width=\"280\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#f5c6cb\" stroke=\"#dc3545\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"495\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Triangle Multiplicative Update\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"510\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    (incoming)\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"525\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">\n                    r\u00d7r\u00d7c_z \u2192 r\u00d7r\u00d7c_z\n                </text>\n                \n                <!-- Triangle Self-Attention (starting) -->\n                <rect x=\"1200\" y=\"550\" width=\"280\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#e2e3e5\" stroke=\"#6c757d\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"575\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Triangle Self-Attention\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"590\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    (starting node)\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"605\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">\n                    r\u00d7r\u00d7c_z \u2192 r\u00d7r\u00d7c_z\n                </text>\n                \n                <!-- Triangle Self-Attention (ending) -->\n                <rect x=\"1200\" y=\"630\" width=\"280\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#d6d8db\" stroke=\"#6c757d\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"655\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Triangle Self-Attention\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"670\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    (ending node)\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"685\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">\n                    r\u00d7r\u00d7c_z \u2192 r\u00d7r\u00d7c_z\n                </text>\n                \n                <!-- Pair Transition -->\n                <rect x=\"1200\" y=\"710\" width=\"280\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#fff2cc\" stroke=\"#ffc107\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"740\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Pair Transition\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"1340\" y=\"760\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">\n                    r\u00d7r\u00d7c_z \u2192 r\u00d7r\u00d7c_z\n                </text>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- Central Communication Block -->\n            <g id=\"communication\">\n                <!-- Outer Product Mean -->\n                <rect x=\"600\" y=\"400\" width=\"200\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#e1f5fe\" stroke=\"#0277bd\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"700\" y=\"425\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Outer Product\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"700\" y=\"445\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                    Mean\n                </text>\n                <text x=\"700\" y=\"465\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">\n                    s\u00d7r\u00d7c_m \u2192 r\u00d7r\u00d7c_z\n                </text>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- Arrows -->\n            <defs>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                </marker>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead-blue\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#0277bd\"/>\n                </marker>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead-orange\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#f39c12\"/>\n                </marker>\n            </defs>\n            \n            <!-- MSA to Outer Product Mean -->\n            <path d=\"M 420 260 Q 500 260 580 440\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0277bd\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-blue)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Outer Product Mean to Pair -->\n            <path d=\"M 820 440 Q 900 440 1180 260\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0277bd\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-blue)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Pair bias to MSA Row Attention -->\n            <path d=\"M 1180 260 Q 1100 260 1020 350 Q 940 440 860 430 Q 780 420 440 430\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-orange)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Vertical flow arrows in MSA -->\n            <path d=\"M 280 370 L 280 380\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <path d=\"M 280 480 L 280 480\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <path d=\"M 280 580 L 280 580\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Vertical flow arrows in Pair -->\n            <path d=\"M 1340 370 L 1340 380\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <path d=\"M 1340 460 L 1340 460\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <path d=\"M 1340 540 L 1340 540\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <path d=\"M 1340 620 L 1340 620\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <path d=\"M 1340 700 L 1340 700\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Block repetition indicator -->\n            <rect x=\"1520\" y=\"100\" width=\"120\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#f1f3f4\" stroke=\"#5f6368\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"1580\" y=\"125\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                Repeat\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"1580\" y=\"145\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#e91e63\">\n                \u00d748\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Legend -->\n            <rect x=\"1650\" y=\"200\" width=\"200\" height=\"400\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"1750\" y=\"225\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\n                Legend\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Legend items -->\n            <rect x=\"1670\" y=\"240\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1700\" y=\"252\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">MSA Representation</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1670\" y=\"260\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#fce4ec\" stroke=\"#e91e63\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1700\" y=\"272\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Pair Representation</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1670\" y=\"280\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#fff3cd\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1700\" y=\"292\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">MSA Row Attention</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1670\" y=\"300\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#d1ecf1\" stroke=\"#17a2b8\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1700\" y=\"312\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">MSA Column Attention</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1670\" y=\"320\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#d4edda\" stroke=\"#28a745\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1700\" y=\"332\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">MSA Transition</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1670\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#e1f5fe\" stroke=\"#0277bd\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1700\" y=\"352\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Outer Product Mean</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1670\" y=\"360\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#f8d7da\" stroke=\"#dc3545\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1700\" y=\"372\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Triangle Updates</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1670\" y=\"380\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#e2e3e5\" stroke=\"#6c757d\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1700\" y=\"392\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Triangle Attention</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1670\" y=\"400\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#fff2cc\" stroke=\"#ffc107\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1700\" y=\"412\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Pair Transition</text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow legend -->\n            <line x1=\"1670\" y1=\"430\" x2=\"1690\" y2=\"430\" stroke=\"#0277bd\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-blue)\"/>\n            <text x=\"1700\" y=\"435\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">MSA\u2192Pair Flow</text>\n            \n            <line x1=\"1670\" y1=\"450\" x2=\"1690\" y2=\"450\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-orange)\"/>\n            <text x=\"1700\" y=\"455\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Pair Bias</text>\n            \n            <line x1=\"1670\" y1=\"470\" x2=\"1690\" y2=\"470\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"1700\" y=\"475\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Sequential Flow</text>\n            \n            <!-- Tensor shape annotations -->\n            <text x=\"50\" y=\"920\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Tensor Shapes:</text>\n            <text x=\"50\" y=\"940\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#34495e\">s = sequences, r = residues, c_m = MSA channels, c_z = pair channels</text>\n            <text x=\"50\" y=\"960\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#34495e\">Typical values: s\u2248512, r\u2248256, c_m=256, c_z=128</text>\n        </svg>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>"}